annotationA: Probable phosphomannomutase; Involved in the synthesis of the GDP-mannose and dolichol-phosphate-mannose required for a number of critical mannosyl transfer reactions
annotationB: Phosphotransferase; Fructokinase activity; mannokinase activity; hexokinase activity; ATP binding; glucokinase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: glycolytic process; cellular glucose homeostasis; lateral inhibition
